        "id": "cybercanid_mount",
        "name": "Cybercanid Mount",
        "text": "(INFANTRY only): Change this model's Move characteristic to 12\", and it gains the Scouts 9\" ability. Remove the INFANTRY keyword, add the MOUNTED keyword, and replace the list of units this model can be attached to: Serberys Raiders, Serberys Sulphurhounds.",
