            "kind": "setLeaderUnits",
            "value": ["Serberys Raiders", "Serberys Sulphurhounds"]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "cybernetica_overseer",
        "name": "Cybernetica Overseer",
        "text": "(+10 pts) (INFANTRY only): Replace the list of units this model can be attached to: Kastelan Robots. You can attach this model to a KASTELAN ROBOTS unit, even if one or more CYBERNETICA DATASMITH models have already been attached to it. In such cases, if that Bodyguard unit is destroyed, the Leader units attached to it become separate units with their original Starting Strengths. While attached to a KASTELAN ROBOTS unit, this model loses the INFANTRY keyword and models in that unit have the Doctrina Imperatives Faction ability.",
        "points": 10,
        "requirements": [
          {
            "kind": "keywordHas",
            "keyword": "Infantry"
          }
        ],
        "effects": [
          {
            "kind": "setLeaderUnits",
            "value": ["Kastelan Robots"]
          }
        ]
