        "text": "(INFANTRY only): Change this model's Move characteristic to 12\", and it gains the Deep Strike ability. Add the FLY and JUMP PACK keywords, and replace the list of units this model can be attached to: Pteraxii Skystalkers, Pteraxii Sterylizors.",
